"&konqueror;’s web browser functionality has its <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"khtml-behavior/index.html\">own configuration modules</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&konqueror;इत्यस्य जालपुटस्य कार्यक्षमतायाः <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/khtml-"
"behavior/index.html\">स्वकीयाः विन्यासमॉड्यूल्</ulink> सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Options"
msgstr "विविधविकल्पाः"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "पृथक् पृथक् विण्डोषु पुटं उद्घाटयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when "
#| "you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in "
#| "the current window."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"यदि एषः विकल्पः परीक्षितः अस्ति तर्हि नूतनः &konqueror; यदा भवान् कञ्चन पुटं उद्घाटयति "
"तदा विण्डो निर्मितं भविष्यति, न तु केवलं वर्तमानविण्डो मध्ये तस्य पुटस्य सामग्रीं दर्शयितुं ।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Show 'Delete' menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr "'Delete' मेनू प्रविष्टयः दर्शयन्तु ये कचरापेटीं बाईपासं कुर्वन्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be "
#| "displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can "
#| "always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling "
#| "<guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् इच्छति यत् <quote>Delete</quote> मेन्यू आदेशाः डेस्कटॉप् मध्ये सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धकस्य "
"सन्दर्भमेनूषु च प्रदर्शिताः भवेयुः । &Shift; <guimenuitem>कचरे गच्छन्तु</guimenuitem> इति "
"आह्वयन् कीलम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &konqueror;'s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
#| "Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
